this is my infra setup for deploying and configuring my personal server on digitalocean with the following components:

# Terraform
- droplet: creates a digitalocean droplet with 2vcpu, 2gb ram in blr1 region
- dns: configures cloudflare dns records for the created droplet
- certificates: provisions ssl certificates via tailscale

# Ansible - deprecated
- common - base system setup
- security - server security hardening
- docker - docker installation
- containers - container management
- nginx - nginx setup

# Nixos
- nixos-anywhere to run nix on my digitalocean droplet
- agenix for encrypting secrets
- modules:
	- tailscale
	- packages
	- nginx
	- networking
	- user

